name: Query
extra-info: SELECT sum(l_extendedprice * l_discount) AS revenue FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipdate >= CAST('1994-01-01' AS date) AND l_shipdate < CAST('1995-01-01' AS date) AND l_discount BETWEEN 0.05 AND 0.07 AND l_quantity < 24;
